{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "task-management-api-v1",
    "name": "Task Management API - v1.0.0",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Task Management System\n\n## Features\n- Task Management (Personal, Single Assignment, Collaborative)\n- Group/Team Management\n- Notifications & Task Reminders\n- User Management with Support Mode\n- Permission-based Access Control\n\n## Base URL\nReplace `{{BASE_URL}}` with your actual backend URL (e.g., http://localhost:5000/api/v1)\n\n## Authentication\nMost endpoints require JWT token. Add token to `Authorization` header:\n```\nAuthorization: Bearer <your-jwt-token>\n```\n\n## Roles\n- **admin**: System administrator\n- **user**: Regular user (can be Primary or Secondary in groups)\n\n## Support Modes\n- **calm**: Gentle guidance with peaceful reminders\n- **encouraging**: Positive energy with motivational reminders\n- **logical**: Fact-based, logical communication\n\n## Notification Styles\n- **gentle**: Soft and non-intrusive (default)\n- **firm**: Direct and clear\n- **xyz**: Custom style",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "BASE_URL",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "ADMIN_TOKEN",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "USER_TOKEN",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "USER_ID",
